{"tid":2262323,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屯門牛注意!!!下午兩點半有突發提堂!!","createTime":"2020-10-29T04:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T07:40:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":101,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"6aeb70165311f703f803bf75013839e0c1b815f4","tid":2262323,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:43:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/18375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F18375&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KilYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=fe69d586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/18375</a><br />\n<br />\n🔴#突發提堂🔴<br />\n<br />\n🔴今 午🔴<br />\n🏛屯 門 裁 判 法 院<br />\n🕝14:30 <br />\n👤少年 #新案件（管有適合作非法用途的工具）<br />\nSource: 趙恩來區議員 (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107233492804621/posts/1469307066597250/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107233492804621%2Fposts%2F1469307066597250%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KilYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=5c66bbfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107233492804621/posts/1469307066597250/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a>)<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n［是日聲援表 (<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/18367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F18367&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KilYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=bf999410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/18367</a>)］"},{"pid":"f69ee26eaedf7c5aeeb94614c0021ee656c036ed","tid":2262323,"uid":354682,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5a0ade8f5f41a7345fa8429866cd386f579f0f","tid":2262323,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:44:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"586dc84a9beb2c44c8814b72fb766e9b5119e7f9","tid":2262323,"uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"#Update 便衣警昨晚入屋拘捕荃威花園J座少年，今日下午法院提堂<br />\n被捕少年控以「藏有工具可作非法用途」罪名，今日（10月29日）下午兩時於屯門法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n10月28日晚上約8時，至少三名便衣警員乘坐私家車停泊荃景圍胡忠游泳池斜路抵達，強行上門荃威花園J座低層單位「執法」，拘捕一名年青男住客。<br />\n<br />\n上樓前，荃威花園J座當值保安員曾經嘗試要求便衣警員出示委任證並登記；期間一度進入單位，現場消息表示未有出示法庭搜查令，之後帶走事主乘車離開。最終，其中一名便衣警員才向當值保安員出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被捕少年已被送往屯門青山警署，與早前屯門一宗社會事件有關。家屬經已接獲警方通知，已有律師跟進。"},{"pid":"c87c5c576949f09f0b8e86d5e91b3631e5c313f6","tid":2262323,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f69ee26eaedf7c5aeeb94614c0021ee656c036ed","tid":2262323,"uid":354682,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/asse