ore":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"#Update 便衣警昨晚入屋拘捕荃威花園J座少年，今日下午法院提堂<br />\n被捕少年控以「藏有工具可作非法用途」罪名，今日（10月29日）下午兩時於屯門法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n10月28日晚上約8時，至少三名便衣警員乘坐私家車停泊荃景圍胡忠游泳池斜路抵達，強行上門荃威花園J座低層單位「執法」，拘捕一名年青男住客。<br />\n<br />\n上樓前，荃威花園J座當值保安員曾經嘗試要求便衣警員出示委任證並登記；期間一度進入單位，現場消息表示未有出示法庭搜查令，之後帶走事主乘車離開。最終，其中一名便衣警員才向當值保安員出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被捕少年已被送往屯門青山警署，與早前屯門一宗社會事件有關。家屬經已接獲警方通知，已有律師跟進。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:46:09.000Z","msg":"乜嘢工具，保鮮紙定保險套"},{"pid":"13fc258641ea6b8cfdf9d319a0e208df856fef7e","tid":2262323,"uid":281054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa3baade64deea81dae1efb6e2597b30c7ca715","tid":2262323,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f144368bae2bf35ddde65b8fa48db54a018850","tid":2262323,"uid":188685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cl